{"tid":183593,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"自動波拉手制「流後」一問","createTime":"2017-04-02T08:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T23:51:37.000Z","uid":27995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"666c24f001121b5d70290090e2e7d9806e5bb8c7","tid":183593,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:07:42.000Z","msg":"想問問  在上一啲比較斜的斜路，一架後驅私家車入 N 波+拉手制  「流後」是否正常？  但入 D 波就無問題。<br />\n<br />\n揸棍而在上斜的情況就習慣入左1波+手制<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望各巴絲分享下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4759a291e8e9499397bd68ef58e2f08bbb422068","tid":183593,"uid":93324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:09:57.000Z","msg":"你意思N波手制拉到最緊都溜後？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ae5dab4e94734b635d2e7908ce13ad50f63d49","tid":183593,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:14:12.000Z","msg":"你入N波點上斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82f7412a39116b6d776be2104018e8c3b7f221d","tid":183593,"uid":41803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"如果停得耐咪p 波加手制囉包無死"},{"pid":"66bfe32e4d5a26a90bed1c1ae8c0c36f73cca6aa","tid":183593,"uid":89032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"上斜入波好似會拖爛波片"},{"pid":"4390b1d7d42d2aa1888e1338a5dc133292a3f420","tid":183593,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"唔知講停車定開車起步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9f210d189ca2cba34f587e094eee436fa3f04e","tid":183593,"uid":43111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:51:13.000Z","msg":"學車上斜燈位，棍波停得耐都手制空波啦。冇理由拉實手制溜後喎"},{"pid":"3d980a64c99cf11ce3fca30492d93bf96d98c3ce","tid":183593,"uid":99536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"拉手制都溜後<br />\n一係拉唔夠<br />\n一係架車壞"},{"pid":"74fddb2b6143ef58382ac9f002c10ece0b994280","tid":183593,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:58:26.000Z","msg":"先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f0d2272dcb3a7c5e8ff3c3a495b4818f4fd1ca","tid":183593,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果在咁的情況下  係咪換碟同迫力皮多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2d7be0ab6d4688576c1a2327e1d2f40c92da82","tid":183593,"uid":99536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁即係架車壞<br />\n快d去整"},{"pid":"a3ec87602096d9e120c28c040e3c76a9508668be","tid":183593,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驗車你都過唔到呀快手去車房啦"},{"pid":"cadbe75930d6a36f11072449d699ff5289a279b9","tid":183593,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自動波斜路入N波拉hand break 不嬲都會流後。斜路就踩break算啦"},{"pid":"7c12037e5e42063ffc2054645ec796d53fb9eaff","tid":183593,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"代表你要整brake"},{"pid":"383fbbb9c82e297513a07b6653dd32376f6a0b43","tid":183593,"uid":52591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:18:24.000Z","msg":"向後chok一下正常"},{"pid":"0775bab10639754dcfa6b31b52aa29ff868e9ec3","tid":183593,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>向後chok一下正常</blockquote><br />\n向後chok嗰下學車勁有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f67afbeda5d0bbb85922b04ab2542a92c65393b","tid":183593,"uid":40880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nzip下手制未得囉"},{"pid":"70dd291c9b8ff01f8eb51b31fcb254314c91013a","tid":183593,"uid":93324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係咁架車就要zip手制 入D波唔溜後只代表你用引擎驅重力抵消左令你溜後嘅地心吸力 唔正常<br />\n<br />\nBtw 巴打你話揸棍波上斜拉手制入一波係咩玩法？熄左匙先要入一波？"},{"pid":"ce1dde1b0e648f695c4369737c20faf1a054b9be","tid":183593,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係咁架車就要zip手制 入D波唔溜後只代表你用引擎驅重力抵消左令你溜後嘅地心吸力 唔正常<br />\n<br />\nBtw 巴打你話揸棍波上斜拉手制入一波係咩玩法？熄左匙先要入一波？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熄哂匙   怕流後"},{"pid":"2d275f2eb9c4efc9d08beb1945287deb790acfe9","tid":183593,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nzip下手制未得囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nzip手制都有聽過  但原全零認知  去一般車房人工大約咩價位（怕比人斬到成頸血）"},{"pid":"fbf7b25b926d2c31e2f049398e8b8e5382b9367f","tid":183593,"uid":83471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T19:00:40.000Z","msg":"zip返高個手制"},{"pid":"56f96a52a94519a9d4f4376cf25a467f3cf196c4","tid":183593,"uid":69218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T19:19:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係咁架車就要zip手制 入D波唔溜後只代表你用引擎驅重力抵消左令你溜後嘅地心吸力 唔正常<br />\n<br />\nBtw 巴打你話揸棍波上斜拉手制入一波係咩玩法？熄左匙先要入一波？</blockquote><br />\n做學神果時，我個師傅都係咁教"},{"pid":"aa9f6620eb7dcd482c16f4602e314cd2883f8e02","tid":183593,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T19:34:18.000Z","msg":"咁樣樣架車停斜路會唔會郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abda18d67da8d8c3371db7d96e2c514216985975","tid":183593,"uid":21210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T21:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先講句sorry 講到1999<br />\n<br />\n情況係： 上斜停定，一架後驅AT 入 N + hand break（拉盡）  之後出現流後情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自動波斜路入N波拉hand break 不嬲都會流後。斜路就踩break算啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁請問個手制仲有咩作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b46701de127887a0dff2228c6723d0c11d7eaf","tid":183593,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T03:20:49.000Z","msg":"拉手制都溜後係咪架車壞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理論上拉左手制架載就唔會郁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}